-- Moody’s Lowers Abanka’s Sovereign-Backed Debt, Outlook Negative
-- B y   G o r d a n a   F i l i p o v i c
-- 2012-02-20T12:58:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-20/moody-s-lowers-abanka-s-sovereign-backed-debt-outlook-negative.html
Moody’s Investors Service downgraded
the government-guaranteed debt of Abanka Vipa d.d. to ’A2’’ and
assigned it a negative outlook, the Ljubljana-based Stock
Exchange  said  in a statement today.  Slovenia’s third-biggest bank by assets reported an after-
tax loss of 119 million euros ($157.9 million) in 2011, on
mounting bad-loan provisions.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Gordana Filipovic in Belgrade at 
